    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-04-11T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-04-11T18:00:00-05:00" n="343"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d343">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.9131/141: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-04-11T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 11, 1941—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>17. Your 21, April 1, 3 p.m. The Department in conjunction with other interested
                    agencies of the Government is endeavoring to expedite its studies in connection
                    with the proposed trade agreement. Meanwhile, it would be helpful if the
                    Department could receive at an early date the list of items which the Iranian
                    Government would wish included in the list of products for publication in the
                    event public notice of intention to negotiate with Iran should be issued. It is
                    understood that the recommendations of the Iranian Trade Representative in that
                    regard have been transmitted to Tehran for the consideration of his
                    Government.</p>
                <p>Memorandum of a conversation of April 10<note n="36" xml:id="d343fn36">
                        <hi rend="italic">Supra</hi>.</note> with the Iranian Minister is being
                    transmitted to the Legation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
